metatags.og:description:
"The Universal Sea - The Art and Innovation Guide Against The Plastic Epidemic" encourages everyone of us to reduce, reuse, and replace plastic consumption in our day to day lives.

The book presents a unique collection of art and innovative approaches from 500 artists and 500 innovative businesses. It offers best practices and lessons learned by people who have seriously taken action and carefully considered how plastic use can be reduced. The book shines a spotlight on people from all around the world and how the project was started. 

Read it carefully and get inspired to start your own project to help fighting the plastic epidemic!
